Privacy Policy
PRIVACY POLICY
​
We respect and value your privacy here at VGMinds TechStudios Pvt Ltd. and Videogyan Studios Pvt Ltd
​
This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information collected by VGMinds TechStudios Pvt Ltd (Kidzooly,Brainfun) and Videogyan Studios Pvt Ltd( and our partners through our mobile applications, and how this information is used. If you have any questions regarding our privacy practices, please contact us at
info@vgminds.com
.
​
Apps Without Ads
Third-party Advertising: We do not engage in any third-party advertising.
Data Sharing: No data is shared with third parties.
Device Data Collection: Device data collection is limited to third-party analytics; no personal device data is collected.
In-house Advertising: Only in-house ads for our own apps are displayed, via sections like "More Apps" or pop-ups inviting users to try new apps.
Analytics: Unity Analytics is used to track app installations and in-app purchases (IAP) as detailed in the App privacy section of each app’s store listing page.
​
Data Collection via Apps Containing Ads
When our apps contain ads, certain information is automatically collected:
Device and Usage Data: Includes device details, software, operating system, device language settings, Advertising IDs for ad tracking, and IP address.
No Personally Identifiable Information: We do not collect personal information such as name, address, phone number, or email address through our apps.
Voluntary Information: Any personal information provided voluntarily (e.g., email addresses for support requests) is collected.
In-app Purchases: We do not collect or have access to names and billing information for in-app purchases. This is managed by platform stores (Google Play or iOS App Store) or their payment processors.
Third-party Analytics (Excluding iOS apps without ads)
Certain apps may use Google Analytics or Unity Analytics, which collect:
Demographics: Browser language, country, and city.
System Information: Browser, operating system, and service provider details.
Mobile: Operating system, service provider, and screen resolution.
Site Behavior: Pages visited, visit duration, etc.
Cookies may be stored on your device to facilitate these analytics.
