​
TERMS OF USE
​
How We Utilize Collected Information in Our Games (Terms of Use)
The information we gather is used exclusively to enhance the performance and reliability of our games and to gain insights into user preferences. We ensure that this information is not linked to individuals or any other data we may collect. Your information is treated with confidentiality; it is neither shared, sold, nor disclosed to third parties. Additionally, we do not rent or sell email addresses.
​
Compliance with COPPA
Our mobile applications are fully compliant with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA). If we learn that a user is under the age of 13 through a support request or feedback, we promptly delete any personal information related to that user in a secure manner.
We strive to filter out sensitive and inappropriate ads for children. However, on rare occasions, an ad may be misclassified by advertisers, which is beyond our control.
​
Privacy Policy Updates
VGMinds TechStudios Pvt Ltd and Videogyan Studios Pvt Ltd reserves the right to modify this privacy policy at any time. Changes will be indicated by updating the date at the bottom of this page. We encourage users to regularly review this policy to stay informed about how we are protecting your personal information. It is your responsibility to check for updates to this policy and to be aware of any changes.
